        "content": "DeFi Security Incident: ATM\nDate: 2024-04-01\nVulnerability type: other\nEstimated loss: $182,000\n\nDetailed notes:\nTX : https://app.blocksec.com/explorer/tx/bsc/0xee10553c26742bec9a4761fd717642d19012bab1704cbced048425070ee21a8a?line=2\nProfit : ~182K USD\nREASON : Business Logic Flaw\nSandwitch attack,the contract will exchange token -> WBNB & WBNB -> USDT,So use transfer / skim to\nTo get max profit,not good at math so just copy the exploiter's work",
